extendedInfo.description: This is an Election Night reporting application that will present turnout and results data from the 2013 Albanian Parliamentary Elections. The app will present data from several levels, from the national level down to each polling station, and will provide real-time preliminary updates based on data available on the official results site of the Central Election Commission of the Republic of Albania.The application is localized in Albanian and English.
